                                                                                                              ASSESSMENT OBJECTIVE:
                                                                                                              Determine if:

                                                                                                              SA-17(05)(a)          the developer of the system, system component, or system service is required to
                                                                                                                                    design and structure the security-relevant hardware, soware, and ﬁrmware to
                                                                                                                                    use a complete, conceptually simple protecon mechanism with precisely deﬁned
                                                                                                                                    semancs;

